description: This blazing red fire truck is fully equipped to quickly feed huge hungry crowds delicious slices of David’s hand-crafted pizza. Toppings include traditional favorites like 100% whole milk mozzarella, pepperoni, David’s own red sauce, etc… and you’ll also find specialty offerings like spicy Thai peanut sauce, buffalo chicken, fontina cheese, and much more! No matter the size of the event, every guest is sure to be greatly satiated by all the tasty flavors that are coming out fast and hot at David’s Pizza.
name: David's Pizza
